 Tukur Buratai Soldiers have been captured in a video making rounds online expressing their undying joy as Lt. General Tukur Buratai exits office as the Chief of Army Staff. President Buhari accepted the resignation of Lt. Gen Buratai alongside other Chief of Service Tuesday, 26 January 20121 and Tukur Buratai was replaced with Major Gen. I Attahiru to be the new Chief Of Army Staff. View this post on Instagram A post shared by Olorisupergal (@olorisupergal) Reason for jubilation as many claim it to be is as a result of dictator been taken off their head